snippet.textDisplay:
It's a great spectacle, but I think it's a staged pre-agreement between Stormzy and Wiley.
There's no way a video could be filmed, edited and ready to roll within a matter of hours. It takes time to edit a vid, produce a track, studio time, mastering etc.
It's a lengthy process for each element. Even if you did it super fast, you're looking at a week minimum.
That said, it's a fun exchange to follow 👍
